window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>WARNING TO THE LISTENER</b><br> <br> This collection contains seventeen documented cases of reality breakdown.<br> <br> Symptoms reported include:</p> <ul> <li><b><i>Hallucinating celestial beings during lunar eclipses.</i></b></li> <li><b><i>Discovering structures with impossible geometry.</i></b></li> <li><b><i>Experiencing temporal anomalies in Civil War battlefields.</i></b></li> <li><b><i>Encountering glitching apparitions in seemingly mundane surroundings.</i></b></li> <li><b><i>Witnessing transformations of loved ones after contact with fallen stars.</i></b></li> <li><b><i>The disturbing realization that ancient gods lurk in the ocean depths.</i></b></li> </ul> <p>Reddit NoSleep phenomenon Ross Tyson has compiled these accounts at great personal risk. Listening to this collection may result in nightmares, paranoia, and permanent alterations to your perception of reality.</p>"; 
